item.title: About
item.dc:creator: mayhemadmin
item.content:encoded:
Mayhem Wrestling was founded by Cody Whitehead in ____, and has been a staple of wrestling entertainment in Columbia, Tennessee ever since. Every Friday night, an action-packed card full of extraordinary talent can be found competing in some of the most exciting matches around.

Whether you are a die hard fan of wrestling and never miss an event, or you don't care for wrestling but still like to have a good time, then Mayhem Wrestling is where you should be come Friday night. There is something for everyone, and the excitement only continues to grow.
